ChangeLog

Release 2.5 Start 27/01/2018
* Wed Feb 21 2018 22:31:59 +0530 mbhangui@gmail.com 2.5-1.1%{?dist}
Release 2.5 Start 27/01/2018
1.  moved qmail-newmrh, qmail-remote, qmail-newu, qmail-cdb to sbin
    moved cdbget, cdbgetm,cdbmake, qmail-getpw, qmail-local, qmail-newmrh to sbin
    moved system binaries to sbin
2.  changed data type to TIMESTAMP from DATETIME for timestamp column in
3.  updated flash menu for changes in program paths in indimail-mta
4.  svctool - added option to refresh services
5.  svctool - inlookup supervise/control fifo - allow svc -h permission for
    vdeluser POST_HANDLE script
6.  svctool - updated sql-mode in mysqld run file
7.  svctool - refactored code for MySQL db creation
8.  svctool - use .mylogin.cnf created by mysql_config_editor
9.  svctool - use SHA-512 encryption for indisrvr admin password
10. svctool - moved enabling/disabling of services to separate functions
    --enable-service, --disable-service
11. use /var/run/mysqld/mysqld.sock.tmp as socket for mysqldb creation
12. svctool - use mysqld --verbose --check to check existence of a command
    line option
13. restrict userinfo privilege to root, indimail user/group
14. use configure.ac to use mysql_optionsv(), if available, instead of mysql_options()
15. svctool - inlookup service creation, activeDays default set to 7 days
16. added permissions files for openSUSE
17. create ld.so cache for indimail only when libdir is not /usr/lib or
    /usr/lib64
18. set_mysql_options.c - set MySQL options for SSL/TLS connections
19. added error_mysql_options_str() function to display the exact
    mysql_option() error
20. added --ssl, --require-secure-transport command line option for mysqld
21. use mysql_real_escape_string only if ENABLE_MYSQL_ESCAPE env variable is defined
22. svctool - added SSL/TLS paramters for MySQL service, config
23. ProcessInFifo.c - avoid connection to hostcntrl if host.cntrl is absent
24. set_mysql_option.c - use mysql_ssl_set() to fix ssl/tls connection issue when using libmariadb
25. svctool - create env variable VIRTUAL_PKG_LIB with libindimail.so to provide indimail functionality
26. fixed ambiguous select statement in join statement with timestamp column in indimail, lastuath table
27. added ability to use SSL/TLS encryption for MySQL connections. set use_ssl paramter
    for MySQL connnections
28. mysql_options() in libmariadb is unable to locate cnf files without an absolute path
29. LoadDbInfo.c - set mysql_socket for local dbinfo structure
30. dbload.c - pass socket argument to mysql_real_connect() to prevent failure for
    local connect with libmariadbclient
31. vauth_open.c, dbload.c - use local interface only when mysql socket is defined in host.mysql
32. vuserinfo, dbinfo - display SSL Cipher when use_ssl is set
33. use full path of cnf file for libmariadbclient bug
34. BUG - indimail_stub.c:  fixed spurious chown() in r_mkdir()
35. svctool - fix creation of env variable VIRTUAL_PKG_LIB
36. create SSL/TLS config for MariaDB like mysql_ssl_rsa_setup utility for mysql-community-server
37. svctool - autofix QHPSI during clamd service creation for smtpd, qmqpd, qmtpd
38. svctool - skip service refresh if .norefreshsvc file is present in variables directory
